Subject: Re: [VB] shift rod bushings

There should be two holes in the rod. The little round raised buttons 
inside the bushings are supposed to fit into the holes to locate them. 
Most of the time you have to trim the little locating tabs in the 
bushings to fit the holes in the rod

John

